《'''愛·天使·音樂·寶貝'''》（{{lang-en|''Love. Music. Angel. Baby.''}}）為[[美國|美國]]歌手[[關·史蒂芬妮|關·史蒂芬妮]]發行的首張[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]，於2004年11月12日透過[[新視鏡唱片|新視鏡唱片]]發行。史蒂芬妮作為搖滾樂隊[[不要懷疑|不要懷疑]]的主唱已發行過五張錄音室專輯，並於2003年初開始準備個人出道作品。在不要懷疑樂隊休息期間，史蒂芬妮開始投入《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》的專輯創作，作為樂隊以外的個人計劃。史蒂芬妮參與專輯所有歌曲的創作，並與{{tsl|en|André 3000|安德烈 3000||安德烈 3000}}、{{tsl|en|Dallas Austin|達拉斯·奥斯丁||達拉斯·奥斯丁}}、[[德瑞醫生|德瑞醫生]]、{{tsl|en|The Neptunes|海王星 (組合)|海王星}}與[[琳達·佩里|琳達·佩里]]等多名[[詞曲作家|詞曲作家]]與製作人合作。

《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》融合80年代曲風及[[流行音樂|流行曲風]]，並受到[[治療樂隊|治療樂隊]]、[[流行尖端|流行尖端]]、[[辛蒂·羅波|辛蒂·羅波]]與[[麥當娜|麥當娜]]多名歌手影響。專輯歌曲呈現了多元曲風，包括[[電音流行|電音流行]]、{{tsl|en|dance-rock|搖滾舞曲||搖滾舞曲}}、[[新浪潮|新浪潮]]、[[当代节奏布鲁斯|節奏藍調]]、[[嘻哈音樂|嘻哈]]、[[靈魂樂|靈魂]]與[[迪斯科|迪斯科]]。專輯的宣傳包括發行六張於商業上獲得成功的[[單曲|單曲]]以及舉行北美地區的「{{tsl|en|Harajuku Lovers Tour|哈拉美眉巡迴演唱會||哈拉美眉巡迴演唱會}}」。史蒂芬妮亦經常帶同名為{{tsl|en|Harajuku Girls|原宿女孩||原宿女孩}}的伴舞團隊進行專輯宣傳。

其獲得樂評家整體正面的評價，並於[[格林美獎|格林美獎]]獲得{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Album of the Year|格林美獎年度專輯||年度專輯}}等總共六項提名。專輯首週以309,000張的銷量空降美國[[告示牌二百強專輯榜|告示牌二百強專輯榜]]第7位，並於其後上升至最高第5位。專輯獲多個國家的[[音乐唱片销售认证|複數白金認證]]，並於全球售出超過700萬張。

== 發行背景 ==
史蒂芬妮在樂隊[[不要懷疑|不要懷疑]]的時候便已開始以個人名義與{{tsl|en|Eve (rapper)|夏娃 (說唱歌手)|夏娃}}與[[莫比|莫比]]等歌手合作。在製作樂隊的第五張錄音室專輯《[[搖滾萬萬歲|搖滾萬萬歲]]》時，不要懷疑曾與[[王子_(音樂家)|王子]]、{{tsl|en|The Neptunes|海王星 (組合)|海王星}}與{{tsl|en|David A. Stewart|大衛·史都華||大衛·史都華}}合作，並獲{{tsl|en|Spike Stent|斯佩克·史滕特|馬克·「斯佩克」·史滕特}}進行專輯{{tsl|en|audio mixing (recorded music)|混音 (音樂錄製)|混音}}。在樂隊進行專輯宣傳巡迴演唱會期間，史蒂芬妮聽到{{tsl|en|Club Nouveau||Club Nouveau}}1987年的單曲《{{tsl|en|Why You Treat Me So Bad||Why You Treat Me So Bad}}》，並考慮錄製一些把1980年代風格融入現代的作品<ref name="scared1">{{cite web |last=Vineyard |first=Jennifer |url=http://www.mtv.com/bands/s/stefani_gwen/news_feature_112204/ |title=Gwen Stefani: Scared Solo |publisher=[[音樂電視網|MTV]] |page=1 |year=2004 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104203228/http://www.mtv.com/bands/s/stefani_gwen/news_feature_112204/ |archivedate=2009-01-04 |accessdate=2007-02-26}}</ref>。不要懷疑的[[貝斯手|貝斯手]]與史蒂芬妮的前男友{{tsl|en|Tony Kanal|托尼·卡納爾||托尼·卡納爾}}，向她推介了王子、{{tsl|en|Lisa Lisa and Cult Jam|莉莎莉莎與神秘樂團||莉莎莉莎與神秘樂團}}以及{{tsl|en|Debbie Deb|黛比·德布||黛比·德布}}的音樂，其後二人在卡納爾的睡房裡談論了關於製作歌曲的事<ref>{{cite web |last=Eliscu |first=Jenny |url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2005/jan/30/popandrock.gwenstefani |title='I'll cry just talking about it' |work=[[衛報|The Guardian]] |date=2005-01-30 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927160105/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2005/jan/30/popandrock.gwenstefani |archivedate=2013-09-27 }}</ref>。

史蒂芬妮在2003年展開個人作品的錄製工作<ref name="recording">{{cite web |last1=Moss |first1=Corey |last2=Downey |first2=Ryan |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1471367/gwen-stefani-recording-solo-material/ |title=Gwen Stefani Recording Solo Material |publisher={{le|MTV新聞|MTV News|MTV News}} |date=2003-04-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119095537/http://www.mtv.com/news/1471367/gwen-stefani-recording-solo-material/ |archivedate=2015-11-19 |accessdate=2015-06-02}}</ref>。她提及自己曾在為原聲帶錄製單曲、繼續與別人的合作以及以化名「GS」發行專輯之間作考慮<ref name="recording"/><ref name="hb3">{{cite web|last=Collins |first=Clark |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1562569_3,00.html |title=Holla Back |work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] |page=3 |date=2006-11-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020221431/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C1562569_3%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-10-20 |accessdate=2015-06-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Jimmy Iovine|吉米·奧文||吉米·奧文}}（新視鏡的總裁與共同創辦人）說服了史蒂芬妮創作這張專輯<ref name="hb3"/>。在與[[琳達·佩里|琳達·佩里]]第二天的會面，二人以史蒂芬妮的[[腦閉塞|腦閉塞]]以及對個人專輯的恐懼為主題創作了一首歌曲。這首歌後來成為歌曲《[[還等什麼?|還等什麼?]]》，作為專輯首張主打[[單曲|單曲]]發行<ref name="scared2">{{cite web |last=Vineyard |first=Jennifer |url=http://www.mtv.com/bands/s/stefani_gwen/news_feature_112204/index2.jhtml |title=Gwen Stefani: Scared Solo |publisher=MTV |page=2 |year=2004 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202003104/http://www.mtv.com/bands/s/stefani_gwen/news_feature_112204/index2.jhtml |archivedate=2008-12-02 |accessdate=2015-11-28}}</ref>。

當二人開始創作一首史蒂芬妮覺得太過私人的歌曲時，她去找了卡納爾見面。卡納爾向她演奏了一首正在創作的歌曲，而這首歌後來成為專輯最後一張單曲《{{le|天雷地火 (關·史蒂芬妮單曲)|Crash (Gwen Stefani song)|天雷地火}}》。二人嘗試一起創作新作品，但於兩星期後便放棄了。直至六個月後，當二人再次回顧那些被扔在一旁的歌曲時，史蒂芬妮才發覺自己給予自己太多壓力。當她調整好心態好後便再次找其他創作人與製作人合作。史蒂芬妮再次找回琳達·佩里合作，並獲她介紹{{tsl|en|Dallas Austin|達拉斯·奥斯丁||達拉斯·奥斯丁}}，以及包括{{tsl|en|Outkast|流浪者合唱團||流浪者合唱團}}的{{tsl|en|André 3000|安德烈 3000||安德烈 3000}}、海王星、[[德瑞醫生|德瑞醫生]]等多個歌手<ref name="scared2"/><ref name="scared3">{{cite web |last=Vineyard |first=Jennifer |url=http://www.mtv.com/bands/s/stefani_gwen/news_feature_112204/index3.jhtml |title=Gwen Stefani: Scared Solo |publisher=MTV |page=3 |year=2004 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201084424/http://www.mtv.com/bands/s/stefani_gwen/news_feature_112204/index3.jhtml |archivedate=2008-12-01 |accessdate=2015-11-28}}</ref>。史蒂芬妮於2004年初確認專輯的發行<ref>{{cite web |last=Orshoski |first=Wes |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1485633/gwen-stefani-warns-watch-out-for-solo-lp-summer-single/ |title=Gwen Stefani Warns, 'Watch Out' For Solo LP, Summer Single |publisher={{le|MTV新聞|MTV News|MTV News}} |date=2004-03-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208093404/http://www.mtv.com/news/1485633/gwen-stefani-warns-watch-out-for-solo-lp-summer-single/ |archivedate=2015-12-08 |accessdate=2015-06-02}}</ref>，並把專輯定位為「舞曲作品」以及「惡趣味」<ref name="scared1"/>。

== 構成 ==

=== 音樂與歌詞 ===
《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》受1980年代的不同音樂風格所影響，其中不少歌曲皆與1980年代音樂一樣使用[[合成器|合成器]]的聲音<ref name="slant">{{cite web |last=Cinquemani |first=Sal |url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/gwen-stefani-love-angel-music-baby |title=Gwen Stefani: Love. Angel. Music. Baby. |publisher=[[偏锋杂志|Slant Magazine]] |date=2004-11-20 |accessdate=2013-04-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019162632/http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/gwen-stefani-love-angel-music-baby |archivedate=2013-10-19 }}</ref>。專輯揉合了[[電音流行|電音流行]]<ref>{{cite web |last=du Lac |first=J. Freedom |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/12/04/AR2006120401543.html |title=From Gwen Stefani, A Madcap Mash-Up |work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |date=2006-12-05 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716065824/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/12/04/AR2006120401543.html |archivedate=2014-07-16 }}</ref> 、{{tsl|en|dance-rock|搖滾舞曲||搖滾舞曲}}、[[靈魂樂|靈魂樂]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Stewart |first=Allison |url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2004-12-12/news/0412120421_1_norah-jones-ray-charles-smile |title=Adult contemporary |work=[[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] |date=2004-12-12 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004215556/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2004-12-12/news/0412120421_1_norah-jones-ray-charles-smile |archivedate=2013-10-04 }}</ref>、[[嘻哈音樂|嘻哈音樂]]、[[当代节奏布鲁斯|節奏藍調]]與[[的士高|的士高]]等不同音樂風格<ref>{{cite web |last=Boucher |first=Geoff |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2005/dec/24/entertainment/et-stefani24 |title=Love, music and soon an angel baby |work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] |date=2005-12-24 |accessdate=2014-06-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715041219/http://articles.latimes.com/2005/dec/24/entertainment/et-stefani24 |archivedate=2014-07-15 }}</ref>、[[新浪潮|新浪潮]]是不要懷疑的後期作品經常出現的曲風，亦出現於《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》中<ref name="RSlove">{{cite web |last1=Mar |first1=Alex |last2=Halperin |first2=Shirley |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/gwen-stefani-makes-love-20041001 |title=Gwen Stefani Makes "Love" |work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] |date=2004-10-01 |accessdate=2013-02-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408032522/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/gwen-stefani-makes-love-20041001 |archivedate=2014-04-08 }}</ref>，並被與[[加油合唱團|加油合唱團]]及[[辛蒂·羅波|辛蒂·羅波]]作比較<ref name="popmatters">{{cite web |last=Damas |first=Jason |url=http://www.popmatters.com/review/stefanigwen-love/ |title=Gwen Stefani: Love.Angel.Music.Baby. |publisher=[[PopMatters|PopMatters]] |date=2004-11-29 |accessdate=2014-01-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131024040250/http://www.popmatters.com/review/stefanigwen-love/ |archivedate=2013-10-24 }}</ref>。史蒂芬妮亦指專輯主要受{{tsl|en|Club Nouveau||Club Nouveau}}、[[流行尖端|流行尖端]]、{{tsl|en|Lisa Lisa|莉莎莉莎||莉莎莉莎}}、 [[王子_(音樂家)|王子]]、[[新秩序_(樂團)|新秩序]]、[[治療樂隊|治療樂隊]]以及早期的[[麥當娜|麥當娜]]的影響<ref name="RSlove"/>。

跟1980年代的流行專輯一樣，《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》亦以財富作為創作基調，《[[拜金女孩_(關·史蒂芬妮單曲)|拜金女孩]]》與《{{tsl|en|Luxurious|紙醉金迷||紙醉金迷}}》則以描述財富為特色<ref name="ew">{{cite web |last=Browne |first=David |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2004/11/29/love-angel-music-baby |title=Love. Angel. Music. Baby. |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2004-11-23 |accessdate=2015-06-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107133533/http://www.ew.com/article/2004/11/29/love-angel-music-baby |archivedate=2015-11-07 }}</ref>。專輯亦提到史蒂芬妮的時裝品牌「{{tsl|en|L.A.M.B.||L.A.M.B.}}」<ref name="ew"/>，並在歌詞提到[[約翰·加利亞諾|約翰·加利亞諾]]、[[川久保玲|川久保玲]]以及[[薇薇安·魏斯伍德|薇薇安·魏斯伍德]]等當代時裝設計師<ref>{{cite web |last=Soghomonian |first=Talia |url=http://www.musicomh.com/features/interviews/interview-gwen-stefani |title=Interview: Gwen Stefani |publisher={{tsl|en|musicOMH||musicOMH}} |date=January 2005 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060605/http://www.musicomh.com/features/interviews/interview-gwen-stefani |archivedate=2013-09-21 }}</ref>。史蒂芬妮亦推出一系列穿著自己巡演服裝的娃娃玩具，並命名為《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝時尚娃娃》<ref>{{cite web |author=[[美联社|Associated Press]] |url=http://www.today.com/id/14688233/site/todayshow/ns/today-entertainment/t/gwen-stefani-launches-series-dolls/ |title=Gwen Stefani launches series of dolls |work=[[今天_(NBC)|Today]] |date=2006-09-06 |accessdate=2013-02-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202165854/http://www.today.com/id/14688233/site/todayshow/ns/today-entertainment/t/gwen-stefani-launches-series-dolls/ |archivedate=2014-02-02 }}</ref>。雖然史蒂芬妮只是把專輯定位為輕鬆的舞曲專輯，並沒打算製作一張私人專輯，但依然以不少自己的經歷作為靈感來源<ref name=cool>{{cite web |last=Vineyard |first=Jennifer |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1504440/gwen-stefanis-song-about-tony-kanal-to-be-her-next-single/ |title=Gwen Stefani's Song About Tony Kanal To Be Her Next Single |publisher=MTV News |date=2005-06-21 |accessdate=2015-06-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231215611/http://www.mtv.com/news/1504440/gwen-stefanis-song-about-tony-kanal-to-be-her-next-single/ |archivedate=2014-12-31 }}</ref>。專輯的開場曲《還等什麼?》講述了她想成為母親的渴望，而她在2006年與當時的丈夫{{tsl|en|Gavin Rossdale|蓋文·羅斯戴爾|蓋文·羅斯戴爾}}（也是{{tsl|en|Bush (band)|布希合唱團}}的主唱）迎接了他們的第一個孩子金斯頓·羅斯代爾<ref>{{cite web |last=Salmon |first=Chris |url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2007/mar/02/popandrock.gwenstefani |title='I just want to make music and babies' |work=The Guardian |date=2007-03-02 |accessdate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927041738/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2007/mar/02/popandrock.gwenstefani |archivedate=2013-09-27 }}</ref>。專輯第四首歌曲《[[超酷|超酷]]》講述了史蒂芬妮與卡納爾於1995年分手後繼續保持友誼<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.muchmusic.com/insidemuch/stuff/gwen_and_tony_still_cool.asp |title=Gwen & Tony: Still Cool |publisher={{le|音樂多多|MuchMusic|MuchMusic}} |date=2005-07-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060510034600/http://www.muchmusic.com/insidemuch/stuff/gwen_and_tony_still_cool.asp |archivedate=2006-05-10 |accessdate=2007-03-21}}</ref>。

《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》亦讓名為「{{tsl|en|Harajuku Girls|原宿女孩||原宿女孩}}」的四名日本隨行舞者進入大眾的視線，史蒂芬妮曾稱原宿女孩的形象意念是在她憑空想像出來<ref>{{cite web|last=Collins |first=Clark |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1562569_4,00.html |title=Holla Back |work=Entertainment Weekly |page=4 |date=2006-11-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019212745/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C1562569_4%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-10-19 |accessdate=2015-06-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。原宿女孩曾出現於史蒂芬妮的多首歌曲中，包括一首完全獻給她們的同名歌曲。她們亦出現於本專以及史蒂芬妮第二張錄音室專輯《[[甜蜜出關|甜蜜出關]]》的不同音樂影像帶中。《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》涵蓋各種曲風的音樂。其中多數歌曲都受到在夜店播放的{{tsl|en|electro (music)|電子 (音樂)|電子}}節拍影響<ref name="allmusic">{{cite web |last=Erlewine |first=Stephen Thomas |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/loveangelmusicbaby-mw0000258810 |title=Love.Angel.Music.Baby. – Gwen Stefani |publisher=[[Allmusic|AllMusic]] |accessdate=2013-02-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130214071051/http://www.allmusic.com/album/loveangelmusicbaby-mw0000258810 |archivedate=2013-02-14 }}</ref>。製作人奧斯丁與卡納爾把節奏藍調融入歌曲《紙醉金迷》中，並採樣了[[艾斯禮兄弟合唱團|艾斯禮兄弟合唱團]]1983年的單曲《{{le|床笫之間 (歌曲)|Between the Sheets (song)|床笫之間}}》。{{tsl|en|Jimmy Jam and Terry Lewis|吉米·吉姆與特里·李維斯||吉米·吉姆與特里·李維斯}}亦把[[新杰克摇擺|新杰克摇擺]]融入專輯歌曲中，曲風融合了節奏藍調與嘻哈音樂，並於1980年代中期盛行<ref name="stylus">{{cite web |last=Merwin |first=Charles |url=http://www.stylusmagazine.com/reviews/gwen-stefani/love-angel-music-baby.htm |title=Gwen Stefani – Love, Angel, Music, Baby |publisher={{le|唱針雜誌|Stylus Magazine|Stylus Magazine}} |date=2004-11-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331094931/http://stylusmagazine.com/reviews/gwen-stefani/love-angel-music-baby.htm |archivedate=2014-03-31 |accessdate=2014-01-26}}</ref>。

=== 歌曲 ===
{{Listen|filename=WhatYouWaitingFor.ogg|title=《還等什麼?》|description=專輯的主打單曲，講述了史蒂芬妮對個人音樂事業恐懼的[[電音流行|電音流行]]歌曲<ref name="wywf"/>。|format=[[Ogg|Ogg]]|filename2=Stefani-2004-hollaback-girl.ogg|title2=《哈啦美眉》|description2=專輯最暢銷的單曲<ref name="Billboard-singles"/>，以啦啦隊隊長作主題的[[舞蹈流行音乐|流行舞曲]]。|format2=[[Ogg|Ogg]]}}

專輯的開場曲《[[還等什麼?|還等什麼?]]》是一首揉合電子流行、新浪潮、搖滾舞曲與[[放克|放克]]的歌曲<ref>{{cite web |last=McLean |first=Craig |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/rockandjazzmusic/3631975/Rise-of-the-queen-of-kook.html |title=Rise of the queen of kook |work=[[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] |date=2004-11-18 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117014858/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/rockandjazzmusic/3631975/Rise-of-the-queen-of-kook.html |archivedate=2015-11-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=McCarthy |first=Jackie |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/65501/love-angel-music-baby |title=Love, Angel, Music, Baby |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |date=2004-12-04 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151030095705/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/65501/love-angel-music-baby |archivedate=2015-10-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |last=Paoletta |first=Michael |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1BMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA38&dq=gwen+stefani+what+you+waiting+for |title=Mash-Ups, Dance-Rock Lead Breakthroughs |magazine=Billboard |volume=116 |issue=52 |date=2004-12-25 |page=38 |issn=0006-2510 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603181758/https://books.google.com/books?id=1BMEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA38&dq=gwen+stefani+what+you+waiting+for |archivedate=2016-06-03 }}</ref>。歌曲的歌詞講述了史蒂芬妮對展開個人音樂事業的恐懼<ref name="wywf">{{cite web |last=Vineyard |first=Jennifer |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1493633/gwen-stefanis-debut-solo-lp-inspired-by-insecurity-and-japan/ |title=Gwen Stefani's Debut Solo LP Inspired By Insecurity And Japan |publisher=MTV News |date=2004-11-10 |accessdate=2015-06-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150127035059/http://www.mtv.com/news/1493633/gwen-stefanis-debut-solo-lp-inspired-by-insecurity-and-japan/ |archivedate=2015-01-27 }}</ref>。《[[拜金女孩_(關·史蒂芬妮單曲)|拜金女孩]]》與說唱歌手{{tsl|en|Eve (rapper)|夏娃 (說唱歌手)|夏娃}}進行合作，是一首{{tsl|en|dancehall|舞場雷鬼||舞場雷鬼}}與[[雷鬼音樂|雷鬼]]風格的歌曲。歌曲重新製作了組合{{tsl|en|Louchie Lou & Michie One||Louchie Lou & Michie One}}1994年的歌曲《If I Was a Rich Girl》，並插入了1964年的音樂劇「{{tsl|en|Fiddler on the Roof|屋頂上的提琴手}}」的歌曲《{{tsl|en|If I Were a Rich Man (song)|If I Were a Rich Man}}》<ref name="scared3"/>。{{tsl|en|The Neptunes|海王星 (組合)|海王星}}製作的歌曲《{{tsl|en|Hollaback Girl|哈啦美眉}}》結合了1980年代的[[嘻哈音樂|嘻哈音樂]]與[[舞曲|舞曲]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/pages/gwenstefanix28x04x05 |title=Gwen Stefani – Hollaback Girl – Video Streams |publisher={{tsl|en|Contactmusic.com|Contactmusic.com}} |date=2005-04-28 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208002221/http://www.contactmusic.com/pages/gwenstefanix28x04x05 |archivedate=2015-12-08 }}</ref>。歌詞為對[[油漬搖滾|油漬搖滾]]歌手[[寇特妮·洛芙|寇特妮·洛芙]]指她像個[[啦啦隊|啦啦隊隊長]]的負面評語的回應<ref>{{cite magazine |last=Rubenstein |first=Atoosa |date=August 2004 |title=Courtney Love speaks about Gwen Stefani |magazine=[[17_(美國雜誌)|Seventeen]] |page=19 |issn=0037-301X}}</ref>。

第四首歌曲《[[超酷|超酷]]》敍述了史蒂芬妮與{{tsl|en|Tony Kanal|托尼·卡納爾}}以往的關係<ref name="cool"/>，曲風為新浪潮與[[流行電音|流行電音]]<ref name="ew"/>。歌曲被拿來與[[辛蒂·羅波|辛蒂·羅波]]及[[麥當娜|麥當娜]]1980年代的歌曲作比較<ref name="popmatters"/><ref name="playlouder">{{cite web|last=Smirke |first=Richard |url=http://playlouder.com/review/+loveangelmusicba/ |title=Gwen Stefani: ''Love. Angel. Music. Baby'' (2004) review |publisher={{tsl|en|Playlouder||Playlouder}} |date=2004-11-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20041124015247/http://playlouder.com/review/%2Bloveangelmusicba/ |archivedate=2004-11-24 |accessdate=2007-03-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。第五首歌曲《泡沫電流》是一首{{tsl|en|electro (music)|電子 (音樂)|電子}}歌曲，並獲{{tsl|en|André 3000|安德烈 3000|}}以尊尼·沃徹的名義客串合唱。歌曲的歌詞講述二人在[[汽車戲院|汽車戲院]]交歡，並獲樂評家整體正面的評價，包括拿來與1978年電影「[[油脂_(電影)|油脂]]」及其1982年的續集「{{tsl|en|Grease 2|油脂2}}」作比較<ref>{{cite news |last=McCroy |first=Winnie |url=http://thevillager.com/villager_88/asoundthatpops.html |title=A sound that pops, and more |newspaper={{le|The Villager (曼哈頓)|The Villager (Manhattan)|The Villager}} |volume=74 |issue=35 |date=January 5–11, 2005 |issn=0042-6202 |accessdate=2007-03-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070623144337/http://www.thevillager.com/villager_88/asoundthatpops.html |archivedate=2007-06-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Linden |first=Amy |url=http://www.villagevoice.com/music/the-80s-girl-inside-reveals-more-doubts-than-boundaries-6398906 |title=The '80s Girl Inside Reveals More Doubts Than Boundaries |work={{le|村聲|The Village Voice|The Village Voice}} |date=2004-12-13 |accessdate=2015-11-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117030441/http://www.villagevoice.com/music/the-80s-girl-inside-reveals-more-doubts-than-boundaries-6398906 |archivedate=2015-11-17 }}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Luxurious|紙醉金迷||紙醉金迷}}》是一首受1990年代影響的節奏藍調歌曲，歌詞講述渴望在愛中變得富有，同時把史蒂芬妮的情人與奢侈品作比較<ref>{{cite web |last=Frederick |first=Brendan |url=http://www.complex.com/music/2013/08/best-r-and-b-songs-by-white-singers-in-the-2000s/gwen-stefani-luxurious |title=The Best R&B Songs by White Singers in the 2000s |work={{le|Complex (雜誌)|Complex (magazine)|Complex}} |date=2013-08-28 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151207222201/http://www.complex.com/music/2013/08/best-r-and-b-songs-by-white-singers-in-the-2000s/gwen-stefani-luxurious |archivedate=2015-12-07 }}</ref><ref name="luxurious">{{cite web |last=Moss |first=Corey |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1512621/for-gwen-stefani-egyptian-cotton-is-something-like-love/ |title=For Gwen Stefani, Egyptian Cotton Is Something Like Love |publisher=MTV News |date=2005-11-01 |accessdate=2015-06-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226132800/http://www.mtv.com/news/1512621/for-gwen-stefani-egyptian-cotton-is-something-like-love/ |archivedate=2014-12-26 }}</ref>。第七首歌曲《{{tsl|en|Harajuku Girls (song)|原宿少女隊}}》是一首向[[東京都|東京]]街頭文化致敬的流行電音歌曲<ref>{{cite web |last=du Lac |first=J. Freedom |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/11/06/AR2005110601287.html |title=Gwen Stefani's Patriot Center Fashion Show |work=The Washington Post |date=2005-11-07 |accessdate=2014-01-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208084618/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2005/11/06/AR2005110601287.html |archivedate=2015-12-08 }}</ref>，由吉米·吉姆與特里·李維斯負責製作<ref name="popmatters"/>。

《{{le|天雷地火 (關·史蒂芬妮單曲)|Crash (Gwen Stefani song)|天雷地火}}》是一首把[[汽車|汽車]]比喻為戀愛關係的{{tsl|en|electroclash|電音撞擊}}歌曲<ref name="slant"/><ref>{{cite web |last=Usinger |first=Mike |url=https://www.straight.com/article/gwen-stefani-love-angel-music-baby |title=Gwen Stefani – Love. Angel. Music. Baby. |work={{tsl|en|The Georgia Straight||The Georgia Straight}} |date=2004-11-25 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208031057/http://www.straight.com/article/gwen-stefani-love-angel-music-baby |archivedate=2015-12-08 }}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|The Real Thing (Gwen Stefani song)|愛是真的||愛是真的}}》被形容為是一首舊式{{tsl|en|Europop|歐洲流行}}歌曲<ref name="slant"/>，並迎來[[新秩序_(樂團)|新秩序]]的主唱{{tsl|en|Bernard Sumner|貝爾納·薩姆納}}與貝斯手{{tsl|en|Peter Hook|彼得·胡克}}的客串<ref>{{cite web |last=Cohen |first=Jonathan |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/65970/stefani-gets-a-lift-from-new-order-eve-dre |title=Stefani Gets A Lift From New Order, Eve, Dre |work=Billboard |date=2004-10-22 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151122010905/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/65970/stefani-gets-a-lift-from-new-order-eve-dre |archivedate=2015-11-22 }}</ref>。第十首歌曲《{{tsl|en|Serious (Gwen Stefani song)|認真 (關·史蒂芬妮歌曲)|認真}}》是一首流行電音歌曲<ref>{{cite web |last=Rosa |first=Christopher |url=http://www.vh1.com/news/216652/music-videos-that-never-saw-the-light-of-day/ |title=8 Amazing Unreleased Music Videos That We Really Need To See |publisher=[[VH1|VH1]] |date=2015-10-21 |accessdate=2015-11-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151128012655/http://www.vh1.com/news/216652/music-videos-that-never-saw-the-light-of-day/ |archivedate=2015-11-28 }}</ref>，並被拿來與麥當娜1980年代早期的作品比較<ref name="BBCreview"/>。歌曲拍攝了音樂錄像帶，但官方從未正式發佈，只有在2006年10月在[[YouTube|YouTube]]流傳了部分片段<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.spin.com/2006/10/new-gwen-video-youtube/ |title=New Gwen Video on YouTube |work=[[Spin_(雜誌)|Spin]] |date=2006-10-16 |accessdate=2015-11-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117015308/http://www.spin.com/2006/10/new-gwen-video-youtube/ |archivedate=2015-11-17 }}</ref>。《危險地帶》是一首{{tsl|en|electronic rock|電音搖滾||電音搖滾}}歌曲<ref name="popmatters"/>，曾被大眾認為是對於史蒂芬妮丈夫蓋文·羅斯戴爾擁有[[婚生子女|私生]]女的闡釋<ref name="ew"/>，但其後證實歌曲在較早前便已經寫好<ref>{{cite web |last=Hooper |first=Joseph |url=http://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/a9197/lamb-chops-19303/ |title=L.A.M.B. Chops |work=[[ELLE|Elle]] |date=2007-01-16 |accessdate=2015-06-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924010759/http://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/a9197/lamb-chops-19303/ |archivedate=2015-09-24 }}</ref>。專輯的結尾曲《{{tsl|en|Long Way to Go (Gwen Stefani and André 3000 song)|長路迢迢}}》原定收錄於安德烈 3000的專輯《{{tsl|en|Speakerboxxx/The Love Below|大喇叭＆愛亂來|愛亂來}}》<ref name="playlouder"/>。歌曲講述了{{tsl|en|miscegenation|跨種族約會}}，並採樣了[[馬丁·路德·金|馬丁·路德·金]]的演講《[[我有一個夢|我有一個夢]]》<ref name="pitchfork"/>。

== 宣傳 ==
[[Image:GwenStefaniTheRealThing.jpg|right]]

:主題目：{{le|哈拉美眉巡迴演唱會|Harajuku Lovers Tour}}

史蒂芬妮於2005年10月16日展開「{{tsl|en|Harajuku Lovers Tour|哈拉美眉巡迴演唱會||哈拉美眉巡迴演唱會}}」，以宣傳《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》。演唱會只有一個巡迴階段，並在北美地區舉行42場演出，最終於2005年12月21日結束。演唱會的暖場嘉賓包括嘻哈團體[[黑眼豆豆|黑眼豆豆]]、說唱歌手[[M.I.A.|M.I.A.]]以及歌手[[席亞拉|席亞拉]]。演唱會獲得不同的反響，一些評論家讚揚史蒂芬妮在演出的聲音，而有些則從演出的其他方面進行批評。根據《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》的資料，演唱會37場演出的總票房成績達2,200萬美元，而其中20場演出更爆滿<ref>{{cite web |last=Cohen |first=Jonathan |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/56532/gwen-stefani-unveils-solo-tour-dates |title=Gwen Stefani Unveils Solo Tour Dates |work=Billboard |date=2006-12-01 |accessdate=2014-07-22 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140922012935/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/56532/gwen-stefani-unveils-solo-tour-dates |archivedate=2014-09-22 }}</ref>。演唱會的映像其後在2006年12月4日以[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]的形式發行<ref name="AllMusic live album review">{{cite news|title=Gwen Stefani – ''Harajuku Lovers Live''|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/harajuku-lovers-live-mw0001232097|accessdate=2017-04-22|publisher=AllMusic|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180106120340/https://www.allmusic.com/album/harajuku-lovers-live-mw0001232097|archivedate=2018-01-06}}</ref>。《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》的迷你混音專輯亦於2005年11月22日發行，收錄曲包括《紙醉金迷》、《超酷》、《哈啦美眉》與《還等什麼?》等混音版本<ref name="AllMusic extended play">{{cite web|title=Gwen Stefani – ''Love.Angel.Music.Baby.: The Remixes''|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/loveangelmusicbaby-the-remixes-mw0001224905|publisher=AllMusic|accessdate=2017-04-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011154249/http://www.allmusic.com/album/loveangelmusicbaby-the-remixes-mw0001224905|archivedate=2016-10-11}}</ref>。

=== 發行單曲 ===
《[[還等什麼?|還等什麼?]]》於2004年9月28日作為《愛·天使·音樂·寶貝》的首波主打單曲發行。歌曲最高登上[[告示牌百強單曲榜|告示牌百強單曲榜]]第47位<ref name="hot100">{{cite web |url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=gwen stefani|chart=Hot 100}} |title=Gwen Stefani – Chart history: The Hot 100 |work=Billboard |accessdate=2015-11-28}}</ref>，並在國際上獲得商業成功，包括登上澳洲單曲榜冠軍以及打進法國、荷蘭、紐西蘭、瑞典及英國等多個國家單曲榜前10位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Gwen+Stefani&titel=What+You+Waiting+For%3F&cat=s |title=Gwen Stefani – What You Waiting For? |language= |publisher=[[Ultratop榜|Ultratop]]. Hung Medien |accessdate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120509193506/http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Gwen+Stefani&titel=What+You+Waiting+For%3F&cat=s |archivedate=2012-05-09 }}</ref><ref name="uk"/>。與夏娃合作的《[[拜金女孩_(關·史蒂芬妮單曲)|拜金女孩]]》於2004年12月14日作為專輯第二張單曲發行，最高登上告示牌百強單曲榜第7位，成為史蒂芬妮作為個人歌手在美國獲得的首支前10位單曲<ref name="hot100"/>。歌曲在其他地區亦取得與《還等什麼?》一樣成功的商業成績<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Gwen+Stefani+feat%2E+Eve&titel=Rich+Girl&cat=s |title=Gwen Stefani feat. Eve – Rich Girl |language= |publisher=Ultratop. Hung Medien |accessdate=2013-09-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922231309/http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Gwen+Stefani+feat%2E+Eve&titel=Rich+Girl&cat=s |archivedate=2013-09-22 }}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Hollaback Girl|哈啦美眉||哈啦美眉}}》於2005年3月15日作為第三張單曲發行。歌曲成為專輯最暢銷以及人氣最高的單曲，也是美國史上首支突破百萬[[數位音樂下載|下載量]]的單曲<ref name="Billboard-singles">{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/loveangelmusicbaby-mw0000258810/awards |title=Love.Angel.Music.Baby. – Gwen Stefani {{!}} Awards |publisher=AllMusic |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117032505/http://www.allmusic.com/album/loveangelmusicbaby-mw0000258810/awards |archivedate=2015-11-17 |accessdate=2012-07-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Hiatt |first=Brian |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/stefani-peas-lead-singles-boom-20060120 |title=Stefani, Peas Lead Singles Boom |work=Rolling Stone |date=2006-01-19 |accessdate=2007-02-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627215634/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/stefani-peas-lead-singles-boom-20060120 |archivedate=2012-06-27 }}</ref>。歌曲亦在發行六週內獲得告示牌百強單曲榜冠軍，成為史蒂芬妮首支美國冠軍單曲<ref name="hot100"/>。

《[[超酷|超酷]]》於2005年7月5日作為專輯第四張單曲發行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=69239 |title=Available for Airplay: 7/5 Mainstream |work={{tsl|en|FMQB||FMQB}} |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100303172238/http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=69239 |archivedate=2010-03-03 |accessdate=2010-05-20}}</ref>。歌曲獲得普通的商業成績，包括打進澳洲與紐西蘭單曲榜前10位，以及打進丹麥、德國、愛爾蘭、挪威、英國及美國單曲榜前20位<ref name="hot100"/><ref name="uk"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Gwen+Stefani&titel=Cool&cat=s |title=Gwen Stefani – Cool |language= |publisher=Ultratop. Hung Medien |accessdate=2015-11-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205184525/http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Gwen+Stefani&titel=Cool&cat=s |archivedate=2013-12-05 }}</ref>。《{{tsl|en|Luxurious|紙醉金迷||紙醉金迷}}》於2005年10月作為第五張單曲發行。歌曲的單曲版本迎來說唱歌手{{tsl|en|Slim Thug|滑頭惡棍||滑頭惡棍}}客串<ref name="luxurious"/>。歌曲的商業成績不如先前單曲成功，最高登上告示牌百強單曲榜第21位<ref name="hot100"/>。《{{le|天雷地火 (關·史蒂芬妮單曲)|Crash (Gwen Stefani song)|天雷地火}}》原本並未有作為單曲發行的計劃，但其後因史蒂芬妮懷孕而導致第二張個人專輯延期<ref>{{cite web |last=Vineyard |first=Jennifer |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1519189/gwen-stefani-confirms-pregnancy-while-onstage-in-florida/ |title=Gwen Stefani Confirms Pregnancy While Onstage In Florida |publisher=MTV News |date=2005-12-24 |accessdate=2016-02-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222063049/http://www.mtv.com/news/1519189/gwen-stefani-confirms-pregnancy-while-onstage-in-florida/ |archivedate=2016-02-22 }}</ref>，使歌曲於2006年1月24日作為專輯第六張以及最後一張單曲發行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1520583/for-the-record-quick-news-on-eminem-beyonce-pink-gwen-stefani-camron-jamie-foxx-coldplay-more/ |title=For The Record: Quick News On Eminem, Beyonce, Pink, Gwen Stefani, Cam'ron, Jamie Foxx, Coldplay & More |publisher=MTV News |date=2006-01-11 |accessdate=2016-02-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302181908/http://www.mtv.com/news/1520583/for-the-record-quick-news-on-eminem-beyonce-pink-gwen-stefani-camron-jamie-foxx-coldplay-more/ |archivedate=2016-03-02 }}</ref>。

